Trepdiation Mac OS X Readme

===================================
Trepidation 07-21-07 Mac OS X
http://www.planettrepidation.com
===================================

This image contains the full installation of Trepidation. To install it, just drag Trepidation into your Applications folder.

=====================
SUPPORTED VERSIONS
=====================

This application supports Mac OS X version 10.2.8 and up. 

The client is built with no mp3 support You'll need libmad-dev to compile it. You shouldnt run into problems aside from in custom player models.

=====================
BUILDING FROM SOURCE
=====================

If you need to build from source the source code can be checked out from our subversion repository here:

svn co https://svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/trepidation trepidation 

You can view the repository on the web here:
http://svn.sourceforge.net/trepidation/

The CHANGELOG and other Readable stuff can be found in the directory 
called Docs

http://www.planettrepidation.com

